title: Let's Play - Stainless Steel 6.4 - Medieval 2 Total War: Scotland #30 - A war of 2 Powers
description:
Welcome to episode 30.  We make some major changes to the Scottish kingdom.  War will soon be on every corner of the world.  And an old enemy is faced.  Enjoy :D
